{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9f9e72db50","title":"中共中央关于同意外文报刊进口处理办法给华南分局的批复","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"82d31b7050","index":0,"year":1949,"month":12,"day":9,"articleId":"9f9e72db50"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2daf3e79fa","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于同意外文报刊进口处理办法给华南分局的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"c67de7cbe6","type":"appellation","text":"华南分局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"952d589770","type":"paragraph","text":"亥鱼电悉。同意你们对于外文报纸刊物进口问题的四项","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"5018677dd6","type":"appellation","text":"处理办法。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"cce161b0c6","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央十二月九日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"7af3b7514b","type":"paragraph","text":"附：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"4f608d81b8","type":"subtitle","text":"华南分局关于外文报刊进口处理办法的请示","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"a3ea13cb94","type":"subtitle","text":"（一九四九年十二月六日）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"3cbbc1869b","type":"appellation","text":"中央：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"7c139493d0","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）穗市解放后，文教接管委员会曾发通告：凡未获准登记之外地报纸、刊物一律禁止进口，但目前自邮局寄穗之外文报刊，除寄伪机关者必须没收外，其余尚未作实际限制。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"90c9564350","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）按穗市解放前，香港的德臣、南华等报销路最多不过六百户，固定订户只一半，订户中大多数为外侨，次为伪政府机关，一般中国人甚少，而现在我之《南方日报》与沪《解放日报》，港仍畅销无阻。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"99b733c008","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）根据上述情况，对香港出版或经港转寄穗市的外文报纸刊物，拟作如下处理：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"07ff267a21","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、经邮局寄外侨者，暂置不理。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"e3391aab92","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、自港来穗旅客，身边零星携带者不管。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"6dfb347b46","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、在穗要求设代销处者不准。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"d0ca33630e","type":"paragraph","text":"丁、报贩设摊贩卖者不准。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"ef89245e67","type":"paragraph","text":"当否，请示。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"},{"id":"1267122139","type":"paragraph","text":" 华南分局","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50"}],"page":{"id":"fd1b8ee0c6","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9f9e72db50","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}